{
  "chapter_id": "ch_010",
  "chapter_number": 10,
  "title": "认输",
  "attribution_method": "ai_manual",
  "attribution_date": "2026-01-28T10:00:00Z",
  "total_segments": 61,
  "segments": [
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明最后一次去找沈知夏，是在一周后。",
      "word_count": 19,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_001"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他没再穿西装，穿了件普通夹克，胡子没刮干净，整个人像被风吹皱的纸。他站在知夏审计事务所楼下，抬头看着那栋玻璃楼，突然意识到：以前他以为自己在上升，其实只是踩在她的\"遮\"上往上走。",
      "word_count": 89,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_002"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "这一次，前台没有拦他。",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_003"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏在会议室里，面前摊着新的底稿，旁边是没喝完的咖啡。她看见周启明进来，没惊讶，像早就算到这一步会发生。",
      "word_count": 53,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_004"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "有事？",
      "word_count": 3,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_005a",
      "emotion": "calm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "她问。",
      "word_count": 2,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_005b"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明站着，嗓子发干：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_006a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我想问你一句。你做这些……是为了报复吗？",
      "word_count": 20,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_006b",
      "emotion": "uncertain"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏把笔放下：",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_007a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你觉得呢？",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_007b",
      "emotion": "calm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明苦笑了一下：",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_008a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我以前觉得你在装，在忍。现在才知道你不是忍，你是在算。",
      "word_count": 27,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_008b",
      "emotion": "bitter"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏平静地纠正他：",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_009a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "我是在保命。",
      "word_count": 6,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_009b",
      "emotion": "serious"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明一愣。",
      "word_count": 6,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_010"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏看着他，语气依旧不高，却很清楚：",
      "word_count": 17,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_011a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你那些账，一旦爆出来，最先被拖下水的是家属。你以为你在挣钱养家，你是在把家当缓冲垫。我离婚，是先把自己从垫子上抽出来。",
      "word_count": 60,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_011b",
      "emotion": "firm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明的喉咙发紧：",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_012a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "那我呢？我现在——",
      "word_count": 9,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_012b",
      "emotion": "desperate"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你现在按规则走。",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_013a",
      "emotion": "firm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏说，",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_013b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你欠的债，你自己还。你该承担的责任，你自己扛。你以前不是最爱说'男人要负责'吗？",
      "word_count": 36,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_013c",
      "emotion": "pointed"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明被这句话打得站不稳。他想反驳，又发现自己没有立场。",
      "word_count": 28,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_014"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他沉默很久，终于低声说：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_015a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我输了。",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_015b",
      "emotion": "defeated"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏没接\"输\"这个词，只问：",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_016a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你来是想让我帮你？",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_016b",
      "emotion": "calm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明摇头：",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_017a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我来是想告诉你……你赢了。我认。",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_017b",
      "emotion": "resigned"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏看着他，眼神里没有胜利的快感，只有一种事情终于结束的疲惫：",
      "word_count": 29,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_018a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "我没赢。我只是没再输。",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_018b",
      "emotion": "weary"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明的眼眶发热，他硬生生把那股热压下去，像压住最后一点面子：",
      "word_count": 29,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_019a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "那我们……还有可能吗？",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_019b",
      "emotion": "hopeful"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏看着他，停了两秒：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_020a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "没有。",
      "word_count": 3,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_020b",
      "emotion": "decisive"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "干脆得像审计结论。",
      "word_count": 9,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_021"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明点头，像终于等到一刀落下：",
      "word_count": 14,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_022a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "好。",
      "word_count": 1,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_022b",
      "emotion": "accepting"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他转身要走，脚步却顿了一下：",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_023a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "沈知夏，我最后问你一句。你有没有哪怕一秒……后悔跟我结婚？",
      "word_count": 29,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_023b",
      "emotion": "vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏没有立刻回答。她把桌上的底稿合上，抬眼看他，声音很轻：",
      "word_count": 27,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_024a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "我后悔的是，我太晚才开始结账。",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_024b",
      "emotion": "reflective"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明的胸口像被掏空。他点了点头，转身离开。",
      "word_count": 22,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_025"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "走出写字楼时，阳光很亮，亮得他眯起眼。他忽然想起离婚那天他发的那句\"重新开始\"。",
      "word_count": 40,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_026"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "原来重新开始不是祝福，是清算后的结果。",
      "word_count": 19,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_027"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他走到路口，手机震了一下，是催收短信，是欠款提醒，是他以前从不在意的数字。周启明看着那些数字，第一次没有骂，也没有逃。",
      "word_count": 59,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_028"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他只是回了一句：",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_029a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我会还。",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_029b",
      "context": "text_message",
      "emotion": "determined"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "与此同时，二十二层的会议室里，沈知夏重新翻开底稿，继续工作。",
      "word_count": 30,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_030"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "她的同事推门进来，递给她一杯咖啡：",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_031a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_005",
      "speaker_name": "同事",
      "text": "知夏，晚上还加班吗？",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_031b",
      "emotion": "friendly"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏接过咖啡，点头：",
      "word_count": 9,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_032a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "加。",
      "word_count": 1,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_032b",
      "emotion": "calm"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "同事笑：",
      "word_count": 3,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_033a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_005",
      "speaker_name": "同事",
      "text": "你这么拼，图啥？",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_033b",
      "emotion": "curious"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏看着窗外的城市，阳光落在玻璃上，像一层干净的光。她淡淡说：",
      "word_count": 30,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_034a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "图清净。",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_034b",
      "emotion": "peaceful"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "下班时，她没有回那套曾经的\"家\"，而是去了地铁口旁边的小花店，买了一束最便宜的白雏菊。",
      "word_count": 43,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_035"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "她拿着花，站在人群里，像站在自己的新生活里。没有谁拉她下水，也没有谁替她遮。",
      "word_count": 38,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_036"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "她抬头看了一眼天空，手机屏幕亮起，锁屏上是她给自己换的壁纸：一张干净的账本封面。",
      "word_count": 40,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_037"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "沈知夏把花抱紧了一点，转身走进地铁。",
      "word_count": 18,
      "segment_id": "ch_010_seg_038"
    }
  ]
}